div.div:
Input for stress calculation
M(x) : Bending moment at given x location
E: Modulus of elasticity
I : Moment of inertia of the section
y: Distance to the neutral axis in the section
Output
\sigma(y): The normal stress distribution over
the height of the section due to bending moment
